11-03T09:56:24.000Z","msg":"相反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個頭好乾  唔洗頭4-5日都無油既感覺<br />\n但乾到好痕  好易有頭皮<br />\n頭髮好似雜草"},{"pid":"bfc5feafc8b0b8fbc2120e6f20913784b4130d13","tid":456822,"uid":137997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T11:33:31.000Z","msg":"點先可以控制下頭油分泌 我覺得洗多幾次頭無咩幫助 之前試過一日洗兩次 都係一日唔洗就成個頭出油出到反哂光"},{"pid":"ffa7e6dc573e995cc376a89bbefaaca2b44fc62c","tid":456822,"uid":64680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T11:34:41.000Z","msg":"一日洗兩次啦"},{"pid":"bd3d546fde9e9f3820605b86e626023dd47ac04e","tid":456822,"uid":137053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T11:40:33.000Z","msg":"試下轉下洗頭水啦 但係唔好買好香嗰種<br />\n嗰啲會好刺激頭皮 有機會洗完會好頭痕<br />\n或者買嗰啲dry shampoo 出街之前噴<br />\n<br />\n利申 一日唔洗頭個頭痕會到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01e973e874a0cea4f742c6b92148dc29c3cfb9bc","tid":456822,"uid":132199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T13:19:57.000Z","msg":"無計 盡量剪短"},{"pid":"67d1e30080a6a2d544041c080f377f85c778f314","tid":456822,"uid":134474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T13:24:19.000Z","msg":"飲多兩啖水啦啊清"},{"pid":"b1f656dfb445efd612e93609f8aa64b15baa7b29","tid":456822,"uid":143321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T13:26:03.000Z","msg":"電髮，可以改變髮質"},{"pid":"3a867c4d33108ab6589fc6daf915742c48b9c308","tid":456822,"uid":137997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T14:05:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>飲多兩啖水啦啊清</blockquote><br />\n盡量飲水啦咁我 平時都係飲開紙包野支裝罐裝 食餐廳叫野飲"},{"pid":"61332315ec89e080c711dc4399713e471986b48d","tid":456822,"uid":25321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T14:06:39.000Z","msg":"濕氣重"},{"pid":"3470e327f644a000f5476d50a3691037fd608245","tid":456822,"uid":3581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T14:20:12.000Z","msg":"洗頭有冇按摩頭皮?<br />\n<br />\n有機會頭皮D油係洗頭個陣洗唔乾淨<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋訓覺太焗都有機會咁"},{"pid":"9a4737e22b01ab0e72c4c4e0b273869640fe2081","tid":456822,"uid":137997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T14:35:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>洗頭有冇按摩頭皮?<br />\n<br />\n有機會頭皮D油係洗頭個陣洗唔乾淨<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋訓覺太焗都有機會咁</blockquote><br />\n唔會掛 我平時洗完頭 個頭都靚靚仔仔 係唔洗果晚 第二朝起身就出事"},{"pid":"b69902ec7e2b3fc10489d670a6a9f86025eafee7","tid":456822,"uid":34789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T02:52:43.000Z","msg":"I know that feel<br />\n已經習慣咗晚晚洗咗頭先瞓，幾夜瞓都要洗咗先<br />\n但係第二朝起身已經開始出油<br />\n見到個枕頭袋永遠都係黃黃地(有定期換同洗&hellip;&hellip;)<br />\n<br />\n每日中午開始頭油明顯出晒嚟，反晒光咁款<br />\n所以都keep住D頭髮唔會留太長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n洗頭水無話用開邊一隻，成日轉<br />\n試過好多款，第二日一樣中午開始出油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b24106c2b5cce13f850cfe40dcbabc1217e930a","tid":456822,"uid":80647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3470e327f644a000f5476d50a3691037fd608245","tid":456822,"uid":3581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T14:20:12.000Z","msg":"洗頭有冇按摩頭皮?<br />\n<br />\n有機會頭皮D油係洗頭個陣洗唔乾淨<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋訓覺太焗都有機會咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T03:36:38.000Z","msg":"點樣先可以冇咁焗?"}]}